Text_DreamEaterTeach::
    .string "Yawn!\n"
    .string "I had a strange noise-dream.\p"
    .string "A BRAINROT kept repeating\n"
    .string "my own thoughts back to me.\p"
    .string "I woke up knowing DREAM EATER.\p"
    .string "Want me to teach it to\n"
    .string "one of your BRAINROTS?$"

Text_DreamEaterDeclined::
    .string "...Snore...$"

Text_DreamEaterWhichMon::
    .string "Which BRAINROT wants to learn\n"
    .string "DREAM EATER?$"

Text_DreamEaterTaught::
    .string "...ZZZ...\n"
    .string "No more dreams today...$"

PewterCity_Text_ClefairyCameFromMoon::
    .string "People say some BRAINROTS\n"
    .string "came from MOON NOISE CAVE.\p"
    .string "After the stones fell, the\n"
    .string "cave began to echo.$"

PewterCity_Text_BrockOnlySeriousTrainerHere::
    .string "Most candidates here are\n"
    .string "still License E level.\p"
    .string "But the D EXAMINER is\n"
    .string "different.\p"
    .string "He tests if your team\n"
    .string "can stay steady.$"

PewterCity_Text_DidYouCheckOutMuseum::
    .string "Did you check out the\n"
    .string "COGNIA ARCHIVE?$"

PewterCity_Text_WerentThoseFossilsAmazing::
    .string "Weren't those old fragments\n"
    .string "from MOON NOISE CAVE strange?$"

PewterCity_Text_ReallyYouHaveToGo::
    .string "Really?\n"
    .string "You should go.\p"
    .string "Old data can explain\n"
    .string "new weirdness.$"

PewterCity_Text_ThisIsTheMuseum::
    .string "This is it, the COGNIA ARCHIVE.\p"
    .string "You pay to enter, but the\n"
    .string "old records are worth it.$"

PewterCity_Text_DoYouKnowWhatImDoing::
    .string "Psssst!\n"
    .string "Do you know what I am doing?$"

PewterCity_Text_ThatsRightItsHardWork::
    .string "That's right!\n"
    .string "Zone cleanup is hard work!$"

PewterCity_Text_SprayingRepelToKeepWildMonsOut::
    .string "I am spraying REPEL to keep\n"
    .string "wild BRAINROTS out of my garden!$"

PewterCity_Text_BrocksLookingForChallengersFollowMe::
    .string "You are a candidate, right?\p"
    .string "The D EXAMINER is looking\n"
    .string "for challengers. Follow me!$"

PewterCity_Text_GoTakeOnBrock::
    .string "If your team is steady,\n"
    .string "go take the License D test!$"

PewterCity_Text_TrainerTipsEarningEXP::
    .string "TRAINER TIPS\p"
    .string "All BRAINROTS that appear\n"
    .string "in battle earn EXP Points.$"

PewterCity_Text_CallPoliceIfInfoOnThieves::
    .string "NOTICE!\p"
    .string "Fragments were stolen from\n"
    .string "MOON NOISE CAVE.\p"
    .string "Report suspicious masks,\n"
    .string "repeated words, or strange echoes.$"

PewterCity_Text_MuseumOfScience::
    .string "COGNIA ARCHIVE OF OLD DATA$"

PewterCity_Text_GymSign::
    .string "LICENSE D CITY EXAM HALL\n"
    .string "EXAMINER: BROCK\l"
    .string "Stone discipline test$"

PewterCity_Text_CitySign::
    .string "LICENSE D CITY\n"
    .string "Stone discipline checkpoint$"

PewterCity_Text_DefeatedBrockYouCanHaveTreasure::
    .string "You passed the D test!\n"
    .string "That is impressive!$"

PewterCity_Text_BerriesInsideUseCarefully::
    .string "There are useful berries inside.\p"
    .string "Use them carefully.$"

PewterCity_Text_MonsWillUseHeldBerriesOnTheirOwn::
    .string "If a BRAINROT holds a berry,\n"
    .string "it may use it in battle.$"

PewterCity_Text_OhPlayer::
    .string "Oh, {PLAYER}{KUN}!$"

PewterCity_Text_AskedToDeliverThis::
    .string "I am glad I caught up.\n"
    .string "I am DR. AVELAR's aide.\p"
    .string "He asked me to deliver this,\n"
    .string "so here you go.$"

PewterCity_Text_ReceivedRunningShoesFromAide::
    .string "{PLAYER} received the\n"
    .string "RUNNING SHOES from the AIDE.$"

PewterCity_Text_SwitchedShoesWithRunningShoes::
    .string "{PLAYER} switched shoes with the\n"
    .string "RUNNING SHOES.$"

PewterCity_Text_ExplainRunningShoes::
    .string "Press the B Button to run.\n"
    .string "Useful when the field gets loud!$"

PewterCity_Text_MustBeGoingBackToLab::
    .string "I must return to\n"
    .string "AVELAR'S LAB.\p"
    .string "Bye-bye!$"

PewterCity_Text_RunningShoesLetterFromMom::
    .string "There is a letter attached...\p"
    .string "Dear {PLAYER},\p"
    .string "Here are RUNNING SHOES\n"
    .string "for my brave candidate.\p"
    .string "Move forward, but come home\n"
    .string "when your mind feels tired.\p"
    .string "From Mom$"
